cu.explanation_en: Setting amf_ip_address.ipv4 to '192.168.8.43' creates an IP conflict with GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF, causing address collision and network interface binding failures.

du.explanation_en: Changing absoluteFrequencySSB from 641280 to 640000 causes frequency misalignment, leading to SSB transmission issues and potential cell search failures due to incorrect frequency positioning.
du.explanation_zh: 將 absoluteFrequencySSB 從 641280 更改為 640000 會導致頻率錯位，造成 SSB 傳輸問題，並由於頻率定位不正確而可能導致小區搜尋失敗。
